VARIABLES.NAME: session_id
VARIABLES.DESCRIPTION: The ID of the session that must be used for requests like "Think Thought"

VARIABLES.NAME: language
VARIABLES.DESCRIPTION: The ISO 639-1 Language code that this session is based in

VARIABLES.NAME: available
VARIABLES.DESCRIPTION: Indicates if this session is available or not. A session can be unavailable if it has expired or a session error raises

VARIABLES.NAME: expires
VARIABLES.DESCRIPTION: The Unix Timestamp for when this session will expire
